snippet.title: Curse of Orion: Next Encounter (promo video)
snippet.description: A video I made to promote my own mod for Red Faction. This campaign is a personal mile stone that I worked hard to achieve. It can be found at Moddb here (https://www.moddb.com/mods/the-curse-of-orion-the-next-encounter)
